App::Wax 0.0.1
===========================

App::Wax provides wax, a simple command-line program that runs other command-line programs and converts their URI
arguments to file paths. The remote resources are saved as temporary files, which are
cleaned up after the waxed program has exited.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    HTTP::Request
    LWP
    Method::Signatures::Simple
    MIME::Types
    Mouse
    URI

